headline: EOG Resources to Present at Upcoming Conference
summary: EOG Resources, Inc. (EOG) is scheduled to present at the Raymond James 47th Annual Institutional Investors Conference at 7:05 a.m. Central time (8:05 a.m. Eastern time) on Tuesday, March 3. Jeffrey R. Leitzell, Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer, will present on behalf of EOG.

headline: Analysts Estimate SM Energy (SM) to Report a Decline in Earnings: What to Look Out for
summary: SM Energy (SM) doesn't possess the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely earnings beat in its upcoming report. Get prepared with the key expectations.
